  "title": "Retail Merchandiser (FMCG Products)",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Regularly visit assigned outlets to replenish stock and ensure product availability and visibility</p></li><li><p>Display products, information, and promotions according to guidelines</p></li><li><p>Maximize POSM placement and ensure it's up-to-date</p></li><li><p>Negotiate space rental agreements with outlets</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain relationships with outlet contacts</p></li><li><p>Oversee promotional activities and ensure proper execution</p></li><li><p>Ensure outlets maintain adequate stock levels</p></li><li><p>Educate retailers on product knowledge</p></li><li><p>Monitor competitor activities and provide feedback</p></li><li><p>Any other adhoc duties as assigned<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Min 2 years experience in related fields</p></li><li><p>Willing to travel to assigned locations around Singapore</p></li><li><p>Working Hours: Monday - Friday, 9am-6pm</p></li><li><p>Location: Macpherson</p></li><li><p>Salary: up to $2300 + Transport Allowance + Incentives<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>How to apply:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants kindly state your expected salary, last drawn salary and starting date.</p><p>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Log on to www.e-cruitteam.com.sg for more job opportunities!<br /></p><p>EA Personnel: Teo Kai Xin, Joey</p><p>EA Reg ID: R23114229</p><p>EA Licence No.:19C9603</p>",
